{"tid":2507112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［全球排華］加拿大留學生地鐵站被砍，車上有人阻止其他乘客落車救援同報警「這是他自己的問題」","createTime":"2021-04-27T19:41:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T21:19:45.000Z","uid":121546,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"bc8c3c437cdb41c06dfe3ec304dac16c39d3a597","tid":2507112,"uid":121546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T19:41:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/globalnews.ca/news/7810314/university-of-alberta-lrt-station-stabbing/amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fglobalnews.ca%2Fnews%2F7810314%2Funiversity-of-alberta-lrt-station-stabbing%2Famp%2F&d=APk9rvMsCVL9feuIhYiW0hTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=481b1a36\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/globalnews.ca/news/7810314/university-of-alberta-lrt-station-stabbing/amp/</a><br />\n<br />\nUniversity of Alberta international student stabbing raises concerns at school<br />\n<br />\nA man is calling for more safety measures on public transit after being punched and the stabbed on an Edmonton LRT platform.<br />\n<br />\nSTORY CONTINUES BELOW ADVERTISEMENT<br />\n<br />\nGlobal News has agreed not to identify the victim for fear of retribution.<br />\n<br />\nEdmonton police said they received a call at about 9:30 p.m. Saturday about a stabbing at the University LRT station.<br />\n<br />\nPolice said it was reported to them that the victim boarded a train at Corona Station and exited at the University Station, where he was followed and verbally harassed by a man. The victim was then assaulted and stabbed in the arm by the man, who then fled the scene, according to police.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;When I got punched in the face and got attacked by the knife, the guy who attacked me also got scared, so he escaped from the University Station escalators,&rdquo; the victim said. &ldquo;I wanted to get back (on) the train, but a group of people stopped other passengers saying, &lsquo;it&rsquo;s his problem.&rsquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;People stopped me getting on the train and they stopped others from getting off the train to help me, even though the (person) who attacked me already left."},{"pid":"0230be1fdd65c2357a22038b9a0d33138af6fedf","tid":2507112,"uid":121546,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T19:41:27.000Z","msg":"The bystanders also hurt me because it made me not trust the community anymore.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nRELATED NEWS<br />\n<br />\nJasper Place Transit Centre surrounded by police tape after west Edmonton stabbing<br />\nREAD MORE:Another Black Muslim woman threatened at Edmonton transit station<br />\n<br />\nThe victim said he made his way to the emergency button on the platform to call for help.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;I thought it was a public area. There should be security instead of me waiting there alone for 15 to 20 minutes waiting for an ambulance.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nThe victim is an international student from China, but says he did not feel the attack was racially motivated.<br />\n<br />\nHe hopes his terrifying experience will lead to more safety measures on Edmonton transit.<br />\n<br />\nPolice said the victim was treated at the scene by officers in under 10 minutes after being called and a suspect was arrested a short time later near University Avenue and 114 Street."},{"pid":"02decf46c73a74e9e55a73219503dd906cd9f543","tid":2507112,"uid":121546,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T19:42:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaJHAK27ecAtpsu4PyxsnDgQQjnDG4sQXj42HQvhEcVEv?filename=08gukoR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F08gukoR.jpg&h=cd73f051&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRjp3ipD4j4y8KGCNBugPHEJLw1ruzUx4f9fkEDwkAe37?filename=PGOc2Ce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPGOc2Ce.jpg&h=2a98f316&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img s